<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>王昱翔 — 面試簡報</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /*
     * ── Text Token System ──────────────────────────────────────────
     * All contrast ratios measured against darkest bg (#060e1a).
     *
     * --t1  #ffffff   19.1:1  Primary headings, hero text
     * --t2  #e2e8f0   15.7:1  Body text, card titles
     * --t3  #94a3b8    7.9:1  Secondary descriptions, labels, meta
     * --t4  #64748b    4.3:1  UI chrome only (counter, hint, arrows)
     *                         Not for inline body text.
     *
     * Accent tokens (all pass AA on dark bg):
     * --sky       #38bdf8   9.2:1
     * --sky-dim   #7dd3fc  11.8:1
     * --sky-faint #bae6fd  14.7:1
     * --amber     #fbbf24  11.8:1
     * --red       #ef4444   5.2:1
     * --red-dim   #fca5a5  10.5:1
     * ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
     */

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html, body {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #0f172a;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: #f1f5f9;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    #deck { position: fixed; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; }

    .slide {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 5vh 7vw;
      will-change: transform;
      transition: transform 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.35, 1);
    }

    /* ── Backgrounds ── */
    .bg-dark {
      background: #0f172a;
      background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 100%, #0c2340 0%, transparent 70%);
    }
    .bg-dot {
      background: #0f172a;
      background-image: radial-gradient(#1a2840 1.5px, transparent 1.5px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
    }
    .bg-mid   { background: #131f35; }
    .bg-plain { background: #0f172a; }
    .bg-center {
      background: #0f172a;
      background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 50%, #0a1f35 0%, transparent 65%);
    }
    .bg-demo {
      background: #060e1a;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 50%, #0a1f35 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(#1a2840 1.5px, transparent 1.5px);
      background-size: 100% 100%, 28px 28px;
    }

    /* ── Animation system ── */
    [data-a] { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(22px); transition: opacity 0.55s ease, transform 0.55s ease; }
    [data-a].on { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    [data-a][data-d="1"] { transition-delay: 0.08s; }
    [data-a][data-d="2"] { transition-delay: 0.18s; }
    [data-a][data-d="3"] { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
    [data-a][data-d="4"] { transition-delay: 0.44s; }
    [data-a][data-d="5"] { transition-delay: 0.58s; }
    [data-a][data-d="6"] { transition-delay: 0.72s; }
    [data-a][data-d="7"] { transition-delay: 0.88s; }
    [data-a="left"]  { transform: translateX(-22px); }
    [data-a="left"].on  { transform: translateX(0); }
    [data-a="right"] { transform: translateX(22px); }
    [data-a="right"].on { transform: translateX(0); }

    /* ── Typography ── */
    .f-head { font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif; }
    .sky   { color: #38bdf8; }
    .muted { color: #94a3b8; }
    .dim   { color: #94a3b8; }
    .red   { color: #fca5a5; }
    .amber { color: #fbbf24; }

    .ch {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: #38bdf8; margin-bottom: 2.5vh; display: block;
    }

    .num {
      font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(26px, 3.2vw, 48px);
      font-weight: 800; color: #fff; line-height: 1;
    }
    .num-label { font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 5px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 9999px;
      font-size: clamp(12px, 1.1vw, 14px); font-weight: 500;
      border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.35);
      color: #7dd3fc; background: rgba(56,189,248,0.07);
    }

    .bq {
      font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 24px);
      font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    /* ── Story card ── */
    .story-card {
      background: #0a1625; border: 1px solid #1e2d3d;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: clamp(14px,1.8vh,22px) clamp(14px,1.6vw,20px);
      flex: 1;
    }
    .story-card.hi       { border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.4); }
    .story-card.warn     { border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.3); background: rgba(239,68,68,0.04); }
    .story-card.amber-hi { border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.3); background: rgba(251,191,36,0.03); }
    .story-label  { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 7px; }
    .story-title  { font-size: clamp(13px,1.4vw,17px); font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 7px; line-height: 1.3; }
    .story-desc   { font-size: clamp(12px,1.1vw,14px); color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.65; }

    .crisis {
      background: rgba(239,68,68,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.2);
      border-radius: 11px; padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: clamp(13px,1.2vw,15px); color: #fca5a5; line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .resolve {
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2);
      border-radius: 11px; padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: clamp(13px,1.2vw,15px); color: #bae6fd; line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .pillar {
      background: #111e30; border: 1px solid #1e2d3d;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: clamp(20px,2.5vh,32px) clamp(18px,1.8vw,28px);
      text-align: center; flex: 1;
    }
    .pillar.hi { border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.5); }
    .pillar-icon  { margin: 0 auto 14px; color: #38bdf8; width: 32px; height: 32px; }
    .pillar-title { font-size: clamp(14px,1.4vw,17px); font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pillar-desc  { font-size: clamp(11px,1.1vw,13px); color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    .nav-btn {
      position: fixed; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: 200; width: 44px; height: 44px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer; color: #fff; opacity: 0.25; transition: opacity 0.2s;
      background: none; border: none;
    }
    .nav-btn:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
    #btn-prev { left: 2vw; }
    #btn-next { right: 2vw; }

    #progress {
      position: fixed; bottom: 2.8vh; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex; gap: 8px; z-index: 200;
    }
    .dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(148,163,184,0.25);
      cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .dot.on { width: 22px; border-radius: 3px; background: #38bdf8; }
    .dot.demo-dot { background: rgba(56,189,248,0.4); }
    .dot.demo-dot.on { background: #38bdf8; }

    #counter {
      position: fixed; top: 2.5vh; right: 3vw;
      font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;
      z-index: 200; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    #hint {
      position: fixed; bottom: 6.5vh; right: 3.5vw;
      font-size: 11px; color: rgba(100,116,139,0.45);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
      z-index: 200; transition: opacity 0.4s;
    }

    .arr { font-size: 22px; color: #1e3a5f; flex-shrink: 0; align-self: center; }

    /* ── Agenda ── */
    .agenda-node { flex: 1; text-align: center; position: relative; }
    .agenda-dot {
      width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #0f172a; border: 2px solid #1e3a5f;
      margin: 0 auto 11px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .agenda-dot.live { border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.5); background: rgba(56,189,248,0.08); }
    .agenda-ch    { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #38bdf8; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .agenda-title { font-size: clamp(10px,1vw,12px); font-weight: 600; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .agenda-sub   { font-size: clamp(9px,0.85vw,11px); color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── Wireflow feature row ── */
    .feat-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2840; }
    .feat-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .feat-icon  { color: #38bdf8; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .feat-title { font-size: clamp(13px,1.2vw,15px); font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .feat-desc  { font-size: clamp(11px,1.05vw,13px); color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Role stage mini card ── */
    .role-stage {
      background: #0a1625; border: 1px solid #1e2d3d;
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 12px;
      flex: 1; text-align: center;
    }
    .role-stage-num  { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #38bdf8; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .role-stage-text { font-size: clamp(10px,0.95vw,12px); color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.5; }

    @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.3; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="deck">

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
       Slide 1 — Intro + Agenda
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="slide bg-dark" data-slide="0">
    <div style="width:100%; max-width:1080px;">

      <div data-a data-d="1" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-bottom:3vh;">
        <img src="images/大頭照.png" alt="王昱翔" style="width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:10px; object-fit:cover; border:1px solid #1e3a5f;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#e2e8f0; letter-spacing:0.01em;">王昱翔</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px; color:#94a3b8; margin-top:2px; letter-spacing:0.06em;">Product UX Designer &nbsp;·&nbsp; 10+ Years</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 data-a data-d="2" class="f-head" style="font-size:clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 58px); font-weight:900; line-height:1.1; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin-bottom:2vh;">
        <span style="color:#fff;">我是Leo，希望透過這份簡報</span><span style="color:#38bdf8;"><br>可以讓你更認識我</span>
      </h1>

      <div data-a data-d="4" style="margin-top:60px;">
        <div style="position:relative;">
          <div style="position:absolute; top:7px; left:calc(10% + 7px); right:calc(10% + 7px); height:1px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, #1e2d3d 0%, rgba(56,189,248,0.35) 50%, #1e2d3d 100%);"></div>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:6px;">

            <div class="agenda-node">
              <div class="agenda-dot"></div>
              <div class="agenda-ch">Ch.1</div>
              <div class="agenda-title">進入設計<br>領域的契機</div>
            </div>

            <div class="agenda-node">
              <div class="agenda-dot"></div>
              <div class="agenda-ch">Ch.2</div>
              <div class="agenda-title">宏碁時期</div>
            </div>

            <div class="agenda-node">
              <div class="agenda-dot"></div>
              <div class="agenda-ch">Ch.3</div>
              <div class="agenda-title">DeepQ 時期</div>
            </div>

            <div class="agenda-node">
              <div class="agenda-dot live"></div>
              <div class="agenda-ch" style="color:#7dd3fc;">Wireflow</div>
              <div class="agenda-title">Live Demo</div>
            </div>

            <div class="agenda-node">
              <div class="agenda-dot" style="border-color:rgba(56,189,248,0.35);"></div>
              <div class="agenda-ch">Ch.4</div>
              <div class="agenda-title">對未來的<br>想像與期許</div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
       Slide 2 — Ch.1 Part 1 退學 + 靜宜
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="slide bg-dot" data-slide="1">
    <div style="width:100%; max-width:1080px;">

      <span data-a data-d="1" class="ch">Ch.1 &nbsp;—&nbsp; 進入設計領域的契機</span>

      <h2 data-a data-d="2" class="f-head" style="font-size:clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 46px); font-weight:800; color:#fff; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:3vh;">
        那一年，<span style="color:#ef4444;">我被機械系退學了</span>
      </h2>

      <div style="display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:stretch; margin-bottom:3vh;">

        <div data-a="left" data-d="3" class="story-card warn" style="flex:1;">
          <div class="story-label" style="color:#ef4444;">退學 · 沉思</div>
          <div class="story-title">退學後在家待了三個月</div>
          <div class="story-desc">
            我理解到我對機械沒有熱情，那我的興趣在哪裡：<br>
            我到底想做什麼？<br><br>
            由於我對於<span style="color:#38bdf8;">遊戲開發</span>感興趣，所以決定改念靜宜大學資訊傳播工程學系。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="arr">→</div>

        <div data-a="right" data-d="4" class="story-card hi" style="flex:1;">
          <div class="story-label" style="color:#38bdf8;">靜宜大學 · 資訊傳播工程</div>
          <div class="story-title">認真打下的程式地基</div>
          <div class="story-desc">
            計算機概論、資料結構、演算法——我認真學，也大概懂了其原理理論。<br><br>
            那段學習是紮實的。不是學了一個語法就說會，而是理解資料是怎麼流動的、程式是怎麼被設計出來的。
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div data-a data-d="5" style="border-left:3px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.35); padding:clamp(12px,1.8vh,18px) clamp(16px,1.8vw,22px); background:rgba(56,189,248,0.04); border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;">
        <p class="bq" style="font-size:clamp(14px,1.6vw,21px);">
          "在靜宜大學學到的程式思考邏輯——這份基礎，是我後來能跟工程師直接溝通沒有阻礙的根本原因。"
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
       Slide 3 — Ch.1 Part 2 設計運算所
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="slide bg-mid" data-slide="2">
    <div style="width:100%; max-width:1080px;">

      <span data-a data-d="1" class="ch">Ch.1 &nbsp;—&nbsp; 進入設計領域的契機（續）</span>

      <h2 data-a data-d="2" class="f-head" style="font-size:clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 46px); font-weight:800; color:#fff; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:3vh;">
        學會基本的Coding，<span style="color:#94a3b8;">然後呢？</span>
      </h2>

      <div style="display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:stretch; margin-bottom:3vh;">

        <div data-a="left" data-d="3" class="story-card amber-hi" style="flex:1;">
          <div class="story-label" style="color:#fbbf24;">畢業製作的體悟</div>
          <div class="story-title">會寫程式，不代表你的產出有人要</div>
          <div class="story-desc" style="color:#94a3b8;">
            做畢業製作時，我發現那些得獎的作品——不是技術最精湛的，而是有明確主題、甚至是解決真實問題的作品。<br><br>
            我的程式能力沒有問題，但我做出來的東西缺少一個核心：
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="arr">→</div>

        <div data-a="right" data-d="4" class="story-card hi" style="flex:1;">
          <div class="story-label" style="color:#38bdf8;">雲科大 · 設計運算研究所</div>
          <div class="story-title">帶著疑問，走進設計的世界</div>
          <div class="story-desc">
            我開始思考軟體產品的價值，因此產生學習設計的想法，最終進入雲科設運所。<br><br>
            教授的研究方向偏互動裝置與互動藝術。<br>
            <span style="color:#38bdf8;">那時的我，天真地以為：「讓使用者開心的設計，就是 UX。」</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div data-a data-d="5" style="border-left:3px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.35); padding:clamp(12px,1.8vh,18px) clamp(16px,1.8vw,22px); background:rgba(56,189,248,0.04); border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;">
        <p class="bq" style="font-size:clamp(14px,1.6vw,21px);">
          從雲科設運所畢業後，帶著程式的思維與剛萌芽的設計視角，我進了宏碁——準備迎接職場給我上的第一堂課。
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
       Slide 3-A — Ch.2 電競市場背景 [新增]
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="slide bg-plain" data-slide="3a">
    <div style="width:100%; max-width:1080px;">

      <span data-a data-d="1" class="ch">Ch.2 &nbsp;—&nbsp; 宏碁時期 · 背景</span>

      <h2 data-a data-d="2" class="f-head" style="font-size:clamp(22px, 3.2vw, 44px); font-weight:900; color:#fff; line-height:1.1; letter-spacing:-0.01em; margin-bottom:3vh;">
        宏碁為什麼要進軍電競？<br><span style="color:#38bdf8;">這背後是一個市場機會</span>
      </h2>

      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:12px; margin-bottom:3vh;">

        <div data-a data-d="3" class="story-card hi">
          <div class="story-label" style="color:#38bdf8;">市場商機</div>
          <div class="story-title">電競市場高速成長</div>
          <div class="story-desc">
            全球電競硬體市場規模持續擴大，玩家願意在電腦設備上花更多錢。電競筆電毛利遠高於一般消費級筆電，是硬體廠商的兵家必爭之地。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div data-a data-d="4" class="story-card amber-hi">
          <div class="story-label" style="color:#fbbf24;">品牌決策</div>
          <div class="story-title">宏碁重啟電競品牌</div>
          <div class="story-desc">
            宏碁曾有電競品牌 Predator，在市場需求回升的時機點，決策層選擇重新投入並擴大規模——這代表一整個新產品線需要從頭建立設計體系。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div data-a data-d="5" class="story-card">
          <div class="story-label">設計師的角色</div>
          <div class="story-title">真正懂使用者，才能設計給他們</div>
          <div class="story-desc">
            電競使用者有獨特的心理模型與行為模式——外行人很難在訪談中聽懂他們在說什麼。這就是圈內人設計師的優勢所在。
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Placeholder: 市場規模示意圖 -->
      <div data-a data-d="6" style="background:#0a1625; border:1px dashed rgba(56,189,248,0.3); border-radius:12px; padding:20px 24px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:20px;">
        <div style="flex-shrink:0; width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:8px; background:rgba(56,189,248,0.1); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
