          </p>

          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px;">
            <div data-a data-d="3" class="story-card hi">
              <div class="story-label" style="color:#38bdf8;">速度</div>
              <div class="story-title">生成速度遠超手繪</div>
              <div class="story-desc">有人說 Vibe 風格會跑掉——但套用既有設計系統元件，輸出的介面感覺幾乎一致。</div>
            </div>
            <div data-a data-d="4" class="story-card hi">
              <div class="story-label" style="color:#38bdf8;">精準度</div>
              <div class="story-title">看得懂 CSS 就能微調</div>
              <div class="story-desc">難以微調是對一般人而言——精確的指令下達，不是口語模糊地溝通，細節完全可控。</div>
            </div>
            <div data-a data-d="5" class="story-card amber-hi">
              <div class="story-label" style="color:#fbbf24;">唯一缺口</div>
              <div class="story-title">雛形無法取代文件</div>
              <div class="story-desc">不能只交付雛形——功能定義、流程、例外狀況，stakeholder 和開發仍需要一份可查看的文件。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p data-a data-d="3" style="font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#94a3b8; margin-bottom:16px;">自產工具迭代歷程</p>

          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0;">

            <div data-a data-d="4" style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px;">
