              </div>
              <div style="background:#0a1625; border:1px solid #1e2d3d; border-radius:10px; padding:10px 14px; flex:1; margin-bottom:8px;">
                <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#94a3b8; margin-bottom:3px;">雛形 → JSON → Figma</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px; color:#94a3b8; line-height:1.6;">瀏覽器插件爬蟲 + Figma 插件轉換，但倒入後即脫離 AI 維護能力</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div data-a data-d="5" style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px;">
              <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; flex-shrink:0;">
                <div style="width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:8px; background:rgba(71,85,105,0.15); border:1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.3); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
                  <span style="font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:#94a3b8;">v2</span>
                </div>
                <div style="width:1px; height:100%; background:#1e2d3d; margin-top:4px; min-height:28px;"></div>
              </div>
